{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"offset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"of","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"key","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PartialKeyPath","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s14PartialKeyPathC","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.apple.Swift\/documentation\/Swift\/PartialKeyPath"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"T","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s12MemoryLayoutO1Txmfp"},{"text":">) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.apple.Swift\/documentation\/Swift\/Int"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A key path referring to storage that can be accessed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"through a value of type ","type":"text"},{"code":"T","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"key"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The offset in bytes from a pointer to a value of type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"T"},{"text":" to a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"pointer to the storage referenced by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" if no such offset","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is available for the storage referenced by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"text":". If the value is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", it can be because ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"text":" is computed, has observers, requires","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reabstraction, or overlaps storage with other properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can use this method to find the distance in bytes that can be added","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a pointer of type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"T"},{"text":" to get a pointer to the property referenced by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"text":". The offset is available only if the given key refers to inline,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly addressable storage within the in-memory representation of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"T"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the return value of this method is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then accessing the value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by key path or by an offset pointer are equivalent. For example, for a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"variable ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"root"},{"text":" of type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"T"},{"text":", a key path ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"text":" of type","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WritableKeyPath<T, U>"},{"text":", and a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"text":" of type ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"U"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Mutation through the key path","root[keyPath: key] = value","","\/\/ Mutation through the offset pointer","withUnsafeMutableBytes(of: &root) { bytes in","    let offset = MemoryLayout<T>.offset(of: key)!","    let rawPointerToValue = bytes.baseAddress! + offset","    let pointerToValue = rawPointerToValue.assumingMemoryBound(to: U.self)","    pointerToValue.pointee = value","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A property has inline, directly addressable storage when it is a stored","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property for which no additional work is required to extract or set the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value. Properties are not directly accessible if they trigger any","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"didSet"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"willSet"},{"text":" accessors, perform any representation changes such","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as bridging or closure reabstraction, or mask the value out of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"overlapping storage as for packed bitfields. In addition, because class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"instance properties are always stored out-of-line, their positions are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"not accessible using ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offset(of:)"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ProductCategory"},{"text":" type defined here, only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\\.updateCounter"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\\.identifier"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\\.identifier.name"},{"text":" refer to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"properties with inline, directly addressable storage:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct ProductCategory {","    struct Identifier {","        var name: String              \/\/ addressable","    }","","    var identifier: Identifier        \/\/ addressable","    var updateCounter: Int            \/\/ addressable","    var products: [Product] {         \/\/ not addressable: didSet handler","        didSet { updateCounter += 1 }","    }","    var productCount: Int {           \/\/ not addressable: computed property","        return products.count","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When using ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offset(of:)"},{"text":" with a type imported from a library, don’t","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"assume that future versions of the library will have the same behavior.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If a property is converted from a stored property to a computed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property, the result of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offset(of:)"},{"text":" changes to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":". That kind of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conversion is nonbreaking in other contexts, but would trigger a runtime","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"error if the result of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offset(of:)"},{"text":" is force-unwrapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:s12MemoryLayoutO6offset2ofSiSgs14PartialKeyPathCyxG_tFZ","title":"offset(of:)","roleHeading":"Type Method","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"8.0"},{"introducedAt":"8.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"iPadOS"},{"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false,"beta":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"Mac Catalyst"},{"name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"10.10"},{"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"9.0","beta":false,"deprecated":false},{"na